{"tid":1410403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「被狗隻顏射點算？」野餐砌模型清洗心得","createTime":"2019-08-05T01:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:11:25.000Z","uid":272094,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6479ef15839327b2325510e5cfe2dcca5d107a","tid":1410403,"uid":272094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UcSeJ4A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUcSeJ4A.png&h=4da6d9e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用呢隻mr. Color thinner 清洗亞加力油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWDtOtP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWDtOtP.png&h=6cd526fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tE4EaHb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtE4EaHb.png&h=02d37361&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iSu1o2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiSu1o2c.png&h=95aae5d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtgWcVy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtgWcVy.png&h=6edd5687&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yzXye8U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyzXye8U.png&h=ec48fab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先把開油水倒上化妝棉一至兩秒（好似落妝咁），然後於顏料上來回抹走，總共清潔了三次就可以完全清洗，最後用清水洗淨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmbCGRJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmbCGRJ.png&h=cd24b18c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如遇上法瑯油就用tamiya x20開油水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89kPxYu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89kPxYu.png&h=cee1b914&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c92a1RQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc92a1RQ.png&h=7322633e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E75v1RR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE75v1RR.png&h=c1b863c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三張已經完全清潔，建議所有模型發燒友兩支都帶，及帶大量化妝棉以應付清潔不同顏料<br />\n<br />\n希望資料有用幫到手"},{"pid":"912c321540d74c189ef000448e1d349e2b9a6033","tid":1410403,"uid":268331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"但係咪淨係適用於皮膚上面？<br />\n可唔可以整乾淨埋件衫，<br />\n有時候砌模型會整污糟件衫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d647336f5a582a1befca87de73f71836a93f64af","tid":1410403,"uid":266289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66pgXos.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66pgXos.png&h=8ac89dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9q4mP7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9q4mP7.png&h=efab8691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLFsjBR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLFsjBR.png&h=fb9bb273&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dj1o3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dj1o3w.png&h=59ad9c2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c35e8ce2b078c197603cb9ec56a268e7e5ce2c3","tid":1410403,"uid":46862,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"912c321540d74c189ef000448e1d349e2b9a6033","tid":1410403,"uid":268331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"但係咪淨係適用於皮膚上面？<br />\n可唔可以整乾淨埋件衫，<br />\n有時候砌模型會整污糟件衫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:49:18.000Z","msg":"換衫啦&hellip;<br />\n污糟左直接掉"},{"pid":"f064ffd7adce28dcc70dd9f9a40ce94f400544f8","tid":1410403,"uid":41308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:49:37.000Z","msg":"皮膚過敏 濕疹者小心<br />\n<br />\n同埋係易燃品 小心燒到自己"},{"pid":"beb555a351d2b071b71b61984d4e322a5129af88","tid":1410403,"uid":268642,"l